The '''Glitannai Esplanade''' was located in [[Galactic City/Legends|Galactic City]], [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was one of the planet's most storied avenues, running along the broad-topped buildings of [[Judicial Plaza/Legends|Judicial Plaza]], and its eastern front terminated at the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]]. The ritziest shops and tastiest restaurants were found here. The Esplanade was also host to the [[Galactic Fair]]. Its easternmost endpoint was the [[Pliada di am Imperium]]. It also contained the [[Mon Calamari Inglenook]].

Thousands of uniformed marchers paraded there in celebration of the establishment of [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. It later became the [[Glitannai Esplanade canyon]] on occupied [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]].

